633
00:41:17,185 --> 00:41:18,515
Do not accuse me.

634
00:41:19,396 --> 00:41:23,066
I accuse you of nothing. I cannot accuse.

635
00:41:23,233 --> 00:41:26,113
I have done dishonorable things to survive...

636
00:41:26,236 --> 00:41:29,236
and for all of them, I have ended up here.

637
00:41:29,656 --> 00:41:32,696
No better than if I stood up for myself.

638
00:41:33,410 --> 00:41:35,620
God, forgive me.

639
00:41:35,745 --> 00:41:38,575
Solomon, let me weep for my children!

640
00:41:40,375 --> 00:41:41,705
(SOBBING)

641
