no matter she and Emily were flesh of flesh.

688
00:44:42,182 --> 00:44:43,682
As Master Berry's health failed,

689
00:44:43,975 --> 00:44:45,475
she gained power of the household...

690
00:44:46,227 --> 00:44:48,477
and eventually, I was brought to the city
under the false pretense...

691
00:44:48,605 --> 00:44:51,435
of our free papers being executed.

692
00:44:55,487 --> 00:44:57,737
My poor children.

693
00:45:20,053 --> 00:45:21,433
(BELL TOLLING)

694
00:45:26,226 --> 00:45:27,516
(HAMMERING)

695
00:45:36,611 --> 00:45:39,491
I thought I told you to commence
to putting on clapboards.

696
00:45:40,573 --> 00:45:43,413
