These have all been replaced.

697
00:45:44,536 --> 00:45:46,746
And didn't I tell you to get a keg of nails?

698
00:45:47,080 --> 00:45:48,620
And so, I did.

699
00:45:49,457 --> 00:45:50,707
So, you did.

700
00:45:51,960 --> 00:45:54,550
God damn you.
I thought you knowed something!

701
00:45:54,671 --> 00:45:56,211
I did as instructed.

702
00:45:56,381 --> 00:45:59,551
If there's something wrong,
it's wrong with the instruction.

703
00:46:00,093 --> 00:46:02,183
You black bastard.

704
00:46:02,595 --> 00:46:07,515
You goddamn black bastard.

705
00:46:07,642 --> 00:46:09,692
Strip your clothes.

706
00:46:12,147 --> 00:46:13,267
Strip.

707
00:46:14,274 --> 00:46:15,734
I will not.

708
00:46:20,113 --> 00:46:21,323
(BOTH GRUNTING)

709
00:46:23,616 --> 00:46:24,696
