710
00:46:25,410 --> 00:46:31,420
You will not live
to see another day, nigger!

711
00:46:32,459 --> 00:46:33,539
Help!

712
00:46:33,710 --> 00:46:35,300
(SCREAMING)

713
00:46:39,382 --> 00:46:40,552
Murder!

714
00:46:43,011 --> 00:46:44,011
I'm sorry!

715
00:46:44,512 --> 00:46:46,722
I'm sorry! I'm sorry! I'm sorry!

716
00:46:47,974 --> 00:46:49,524
(WHIMPERING)

717
00:46:49,976 --> 00:46:51,386
