This ain't done by half.

723
00:47:01,404 --> 00:47:03,574
I will have flesh.

724
00:47:03,740 --> 00:47:06,080
And I will have all of it!

725
00:47:06,284 --> 00:47:07,994
(PANTING)

726
00:47:09,621 --> 00:47:10,751
CHAPIN: Do not stir.

727
00:47:11,331 --> 00:47:14,581
Do not leave the plantation.
For, if you run, I cannot protect you.

728
00:47:15,377 --> 00:47:16,587
Stay here.

729
00:47:17,504 --> 00:47:18,964
(PANTING)

730
00:47:54,207 --> 00:47:56,037
(HORSES APPROACHING)

731
00:48:07,387 --> 00:48:08,557
(GROANING)

732
00:48:10,223 --> 00:48:11,683
(CHOKING)

733
00:48:20,150 --> 00:48:24,070
Gentlemen,
whoever moves that nigger is a dead man.

734
00:48:24,487 --> 00:48:25,737
(GASPING)

735
00:48:25,989 --> 00:48:28,739
I am the overseer on this plantation.

736
00:48:29,075 --> 00:48:31,615
William Ford holds
the mortgage on Platt.

737
00:48:32,120 --> 00:48:34,580
If you hang him, he will lose his debt.

738
00:48:35,081 --> 00:48:37,381
You have no claim to his life.

739
00:48:37,959 --> 00:48:39,379
As for you two...

740
00:48:39,544 --> 00:48:42,554
if you have any regard for your own safety...

741
00:48:42,672 --> 00:48:43,632
I say, be gone!

742
00:48:47,344 --> 00:48:49,224
You got no cause!

743
00:48:49,346 --> 00:48:52,676
Platt is mine,
and mine to do with as I please!

744
00:48:53,016 --> 00:48:53,726
If you touch...

745
00:48:54,059 --> 00:48:54,979
(COCKS GUN)

746
00:49:08,490 --> 00:49:10,030
(PANTING)

747
00:49:21,252 --> 00:49:22,002
Sam!

748
00:49:22,671 --> 00:49:25,091
Fetch the mule. Get Master Ford.

749
00:49:28,051 --> 00:49:30,051
(CONTINUES PANTING)

750
00:51:09,235 --> 00:51:10,395
(COUGHS)

751
00:51:36,304 --> 00:51:37,474
(CHILDREN LAUGHING)

752
00:51:44,062 --> 00:51:46,152
(GASPING)

753
00:52:13,008 --> 00:52:14,298
(HORSE APPROACHING)

754
00:52:20,015 --> 00:52:22,225
Platt. Poor Platt.

755
00:52:24,519 --> 00:52:25,399
(GRUNTS)

756
00:52:30,358 --> 00:52:31,398
(DOOR CLOSES)

757
00:52:40,452 --> 00:52:41,662
(DOOR OPENS)

758
00:52:51,671 --> 00:52:54,221
I believe Tibeats is
skulking about the premises somewhere.

759
00:52:54,382 --> 00:52:57,552
He wants you dead, and he will have it so.

760
00:52:57,677 --> 00:53:00,057
It's no longer safe for you here.

761
00:53:00,221 --> 00:53:04,061
And I don't believe
you will remain passive if Tibeats attacks.

762
00:53:04,225 --> 00:53:07,225
I have transferred my debt to Edwin Epps.

763
00:53:07,395 --> 00:53:08,265
He will take charge...

764
00:53:08,396 --> 00:53:09,306
(HORSE NEIGHING)

765
00:53:30,043 --> 00:53:31,543
Master Ford.

766
00:53:34,047 --> 00:53:36,677
You must know that I'm not a slave.

767
00:53:37,217 --> 00:53:38,257
I cannot hear that.

768
00:53:38,385 --> 00:53:40,385
Before I came to you, I was a freeman.

769
00:53:40,470 --> 00:53:43,220
I'm trying to save your life!

770
00:53:44,391 --> 00:53:47,021
And I have a debt to be mindful of.

771
00:53:49,312 --> 00:53:51,362
And that is to Edwin Epps now.

772
00:53:51,481 --> 00:53:54,321
And he is a hard man.
Prides himself on being a nigger breaker.

773
00:53:54,442 --> 00:53:57,492
But truthfully,
I could find no others who would take you.

774
00:53:58,154 --> 00:54:00,574
You've made a reputation of yourself.

775
00:54:01,366 --> 00:54:06,196
Whatever the circumstances,
you are an exceptional nigger, Platt.

776
00:54:08,081 --> 00:54:10,711
But I fear no good will come of it.

777
00:54:33,481 --> 00:54:35,361
"And that servant...

778
00:54:36,484 --> 00:54:39,074
"which knew his lord's will..."

779
00:54:40,405 --> 00:54:43,985
Which knew his lord's will.

780
00:54:48,038 --> 00:54:50,578
"...and prepared not himself..."

781
00:54:52,250 --> 00:54:54,710
Prepared not himself.

782
00:54:58,715 --> 00:55:01,505
"...neither did according to his will...

783
00:55:03,470 --> 00:55:06,600
"shall be beaten with many stripes."

784
00:55:08,058 --> 00:55:09,428
Do you hear that?

785
00:55:10,185 --> 00:55:11,435
"Stripes."

786
00:55:12,645 --> 00:55:14,725
That nigger that don't obey his lord...

787
00:55:15,065 --> 00:55:17,105
