1115
01:21:56,374 --> 01:21:57,384
Damn!

1116
01:21:58,293 --> 01:21:59,293
Damn you!

1117
01:22:00,587 --> 01:22:02,207
Damn all y'all!

1118
01:22:29,991 --> 01:22:30,991
Judge.

1119
01:22:31,242 --> 01:22:32,662
Mister Epps.

1120
01:22:34,496 --> 01:22:38,326
