Yes, sir.

1195
01:29:27,325 --> 01:29:29,405
Take them out, get to whipping.

1196
01:29:34,541 --> 01:29:35,711
(GROANING)

1197
01:29:35,959 --> 01:29:37,959
ARMSBY: It's a tragedy.

1198
01:29:39,045 --> 01:29:40,705
How does such come to pass?

1199
01:29:41,715 --> 01:29:45,045
Working a field
and picking cotton like a lowly hand.

1200
01:29:45,468 --> 01:29:47,968
I'm of a damn sight better station.

1201
01:29:49,055 --> 01:29:51,055
I worked as an overseer, you know.

1202
01:29:51,224 --> 01:29:52,564
I did not know, sir.

1203
01:29:52,726 --> 01:29:54,306
Not "sir."

1204
01:29:55,061 --> 01:29:56,731
Just "Armsby."

1205
01:29:57,605 --> 01:29:59,725
I'm not owed
more than any other in the field.

1206
01:30:00,066 --> 01:30:03,066
How did you
arrive at such a place, if I may ask?

1207
01:30:03,403 --> 01:30:06,073
Ask, it's just conversation.

1208
01:30:08,116 --> 01:30:11,076
I became
a little too dependent on the whiskey...

1209
01:30:11,244 --> 01:30:13,624
a little too undependable on the job.

1210
01:30:15,040 --> 01:30:17,580
Now, before you say
I'm just a sorry drunkard...

1211
01:30:17,959 --> 01:30:20,049
let me state my case.

1212
01:30:21,004 --> 01:30:23,054
As reliable employment as overseeing is,

1213
01:30:23,214 --> 01:30:25,264
it is no easy chore on the spirit.

1214
01:30:26,134 --> 01:30:28,974
I say, no man of conscious...

1215
01:30:29,095 --> 01:30:31,465
can take the lash
to another human day in and day out...

1216
01:30:31,598 --> 01:30:34,138
without shredding at his own self.

1217
01:30:35,143 --> 01:30:37,273
Takes him to a place...

1218
01:30:37,395 --> 01:30:42,025
where he either makes
excuses within his mind to be unaffected...

1219
01:30:42,400 --> 01:30:45,700
or he finds some way
to trample his guilty sensations.

1220
01:30:46,613 --> 01:30:48,283
So, I trampled.

1221
01:30:48,406 --> 01:30:50,366
With frequency.

1222
01:30:51,993 --> 01:30:55,083
I gave in to tales of wealth and prosperity.

1223
01:30:58,249 --> 01:31:02,709
But such profitable outcomes are
reserved for plantation masters.

1224
01:31:03,380 --> 01:31:06,550
It's the lot of the rest of us to serve.

1225
01:31:08,218 --> 01:31:13,558
Now, all I want is
to earn a decent wage and get myself home.

1226
01:31:34,411 --> 01:31:36,081
(DOOR OPENING)

1227
01:31:45,672 --> 01:31:47,972
The proceeds of
my fiddling performances.

1228
01:31:48,591 --> 01:31:52,721
Just a few picayunes,
but all I have in the world.

1229
01:31:53,388 --> 01:31:56,728
I promise them to you
if you will do me the favor I require.

1230
01:31:57,058 --> 01:32:01,148
But I beg you not to
expose me if you cannot grant the request.

1231
01:32:01,563 --> 01:32:02,653
Uh...

1232
01:32:03,398 --> 01:32:05,108
What is it you ask?

1233
01:32:05,233 --> 01:32:07,403
First, your word, sir.

1234
01:32:08,153 --> 01:32:09,153
On my honor.

1235
01:32:11,239 --> 01:32:13,239
It's a simple enough request.

1236
01:32:14,576 --> 01:32:16,406
I only ask that you deposit a letter

1237
01:32:16,494 --> 01:32:18,294
at the post office in Marksville...

1238
01:32:18,413 --> 01:32:21,963
and that you keep the action
an inviolable secret forever.

1239
01:32:25,128 --> 01:32:27,458
A patron is what I require, sir.

1240
01:32:34,137 --> 01:32:35,007
I'll do it.

1241
01:32:36,056 --> 01:32:38,426
And I'll accept whatever payment's offered.

1242
01:32:41,227 --> 01:32:43,687
To assist you, I put my own self at risk.

1243
01:32:44,481 --> 01:32:46,401
I will do so...

1244
01:32:46,524 --> 01:32:49,654
but fair compensation is all I ask.

1245
01:32:59,245 --> 01:33:01,245
Draw up your letter.

1246
01:33:01,414 --> 01:33:03,714
We'll meet again in two days?

1247
01:33:05,460 --> 01:33:07,340
In two days.

1248
01:33:10,131 --> 01:33:11,551
Thank you.

1249
01:34:01,391 --> 01:34:02,561
(BLOWING)

1250
01:34:29,210 --> 01:34:31,050
Well, boy...

1251
01:34:31,212 --> 01:34:36,052
I understand
I got a learned nigger that writes letters.

1252
01:34:37,135 --> 01:34:40,215
Tries to get white fellas to mail them.

1253
01:34:45,226 --> 01:34:46,386
(LAUGHS)

1254
01:34:46,478 --> 01:34:49,228
Armsby told me today...

1255
01:34:49,356 --> 01:34:51,976
the devil was among my niggers.

1256
01:34:53,485 --> 01:34:56,445
That I had one that needed watching...

1257
01:34:56,571 --> 01:34:59,071
or he would run away.

1258
01:35:01,076 --> 01:35:02,986
When I asked him why...

1259
01:35:03,703 --> 01:35:07,213
he said you come over to him...

1260
01:35:07,374 --> 01:35:10,254
waked him up in the middle of the night...

1261
01:35:10,377 --> 01:35:13,127
and wanted him to carry a letter...

1262
01:35:14,339 --> 01:35:16,089
to Marksville.

1263
01:35:21,221 --> 01:35:23,521
What do you got to say to that?

1264
01:35:26,393 --> 01:35:28,233
There's no truth to it.

1265
01:35:29,104 --> 01:35:30,564
You say.

1266
01:35:32,232 --> 01:35:35,072
