I got no friends living as I know of.

1268
01:35:40,740 --> 01:35:42,490
That Armsby...

1269
01:35:43,993 --> 01:35:47,413
That Armsby is a lying, drunken fellow.

1270
01:35:49,249 --> 01:35:52,209
