hire him as an overseer?

1271
01:35:54,045 --> 01:35:55,585
Well, that's it.

1272
01:35:57,048 --> 01:35:59,088
He wants to make you believe
we're all gonna run away...

1273
01:35:59,217 --> 01:36:01,717
