1274
01:36:03,221 --> 01:36:05,601
He believes you're a soft soap.

1275
01:36:06,516 --> 01:36:09,056
And he's given to such talk.

1276
01:36:09,978 --> 01:36:13,568
Made this story out of whole cloth...

1277
01:36:14,232 --> 01:36:16,482
