(LAUGHING)

1353
01:42:27,731 --> 01:42:28,981
What's funny?

1354
01:42:29,107 --> 01:42:32,687
Epps, I merely mean to
finish the work at hand, as requested.

1355
01:42:33,028 --> 01:42:34,648
And as paid for.

1356
01:42:34,988 --> 01:42:36,608
If something rubs you wrongly...

1357
01:42:36,990 --> 01:42:39,700
I offer you the opportunity to speak on it.

1358
01:42:43,079 --> 01:42:45,579
You ask plainly, so I will tell you plainly.

1359
01:42:46,374 --> 01:42:50,594
What amused me just then was your
concern for my well-being in this heat...

1360
01:42:50,962 --> 01:42:53,972
when, quite frankly,
the condition of your laborers...

1361
01:42:54,049 --> 01:42:55,219
"The condition of my laborers"?

1362
01:42:55,342 --> 01:42:57,342
BASS: It is horrid. It's all wrong.

1363
01:42:57,469 --> 01:42:58,639
All wrong, Mr. Epps.

1364
01:42:58,970 --> 01:43:01,220
They ain't hired help.

1365
01:43:01,389 --> 01:43:02,389
They're my property.

1366
01:43:03,266 --> 01:43:04,266
You say that with pride.

1367
01:43:04,392 --> 01:43:06,142
I say it as fact.

1368
01:43:08,229 --> 01:43:10,729
If this conversation concerns what is factual

1369
01:43:11,066 --> 01:43:13,566
and what is not, then it must be said...

1370
01:43:13,735 --> 01:43:17,025
that there is no justice
nor righteousness in their slavery.

1371
01:43:17,697 --> 01:43:19,987
But you do open up an interesting question.

1372
01:43:21,117 --> 01:43:22,447
What right have you to your niggers,

1373
01:43:22,577 --> 01:43:24,077
when you come down to the point?

1374
01:43:24,412 --> 01:43:25,622
-What right?
-Mmm.

1375
01:43:26,331 --> 01:43:29,171
I bought them. I paid for them.

1376
01:43:29,459 --> 01:43:31,249
Of course you did, and the law says

1377
01:43:31,378 --> 01:43:33,208
you have the right to hold a nigger.

1378
01:43:33,338 --> 01:43:35,298
But begging the law's pardon, it lies.

1379
01:43:36,007 --> 01:43:38,047
Suppose they pass a law taking away

1380
01:43:38,134 --> 01:43:40,184
your liberty, making you a slave.

1381
01:43:40,303 --> 01:43:41,393
Suppose.

1382
01:43:41,554 --> 01:43:43,224
That ain't a supposable case.

1383
01:43:43,390 --> 01:43:44,720
Laws change, Epps.

1384
01:43:45,058 --> 01:43:47,098
Universal truths are constant.

1385
01:43:47,227 --> 01:43:50,107
It is a fact, a plain and simple fact...

1386
01:43:50,230 --> 01:43:53,400
that what is true and right
is true and right for all.

1387
01:43:53,566 --> 01:43:55,566
White and black alike.

1388
01:43:57,237 --> 01:43:59,107
You comparing me to a nigger, Bass?

1389
01:43:59,239 --> 01:44:02,199
I'm only asking, in the eyes of God,
what is the difference?

1390
01:44:04,202 --> 01:44:05,702
You might as well ask
what the difference is

1391
01:44:05,995 --> 01:44:08,285
between a white man and a baboon.

1392
01:44:09,457 --> 01:44:12,287
I seen one of them critters in Orleans.

1393
01:44:12,419 --> 01:44:14,709
Know just as much as any nigger I got.

1394
01:44:15,171 --> 01:44:16,671
BASS: Listen, Epps.

1395
01:44:17,007 --> 01:44:18,547
These niggers are human beings.

1396
01:44:18,675 --> 01:44:21,175
If they are allowed to
climb no higher than brute animals...

1397
01:44:21,302 --> 01:44:24,012
you and men like you
will have to answer for it.

1398
01:44:25,056 --> 01:44:27,136
There is an ill, Mr. Epps...

1399
01:44:27,267 --> 01:44:29,597
a fearful ill resting upon this nation.

1400
01:44:30,270 --> 01:44:33,270
And there will be
a day of reckoning yet.

1401
01:44:35,984 --> 01:44:38,494
You like to hear yourself talk, Bass...

1402
01:44:38,611 --> 01:44:40,741
better than any man I know of.

1403
01:44:41,990 --> 01:44:45,490
You'd argue that
black was white, or white, black...

1404
01:44:45,618 --> 01:44:48,038
if anybody would contradict you.

1405
01:44:50,040 --> 01:44:53,340
A fine supposition
if you lived among Yankees in New England.

1406
01:44:53,460 --> 01:44:55,210
But you don't.

1407
01:44:58,548 --> 01:45:00,678
You most assuredly do not.

1408
01:45:21,154 --> 01:45:22,494
(EPPS YELLING)

1409
01:45:24,699 --> 01:45:25,989
(LOUD CLATTERING)

1410
