1428
01:46:06,574 --> 01:46:08,584
You miserable black dogs.

1429
01:46:08,743 --> 01:46:11,293
You stand like the deaf and dumb.

1430
01:46:13,081 --> 01:46:14,371
Speak!

1431
01:46:28,054 --> 01:46:29,474
