1432
01:46:29,556 --> 01:46:31,216
She gone.

1433
01:46:33,560 --> 01:46:35,560
My Pats is gone.

1434
01:46:52,454 --> 01:46:54,414
Run off? Run off, did you?

1435
01:46:54,581 --> 01:46:56,461
-Master Epps--
-You miserable wench. Where you been?

1436
01:46:56,583 --> 01:46:58,133
I been nowhere!

1437
01:46:58,251 --> 01:46:59,341
Lies to
your misdeeds!

1438
01:46:59,461 --> 01:47:00,631
The Sabbath day, Master.
I took me

1439
01:47:01,004 --> 01:47:02,174
