1440
01:47:02,297 --> 01:47:03,547
Bring the Lord
into your deceptions?

1441
01:47:03,673 --> 01:47:05,133
You're coming from
Shaw's plantation.

1442
01:47:05,258 --> 01:47:06,508
-No!
-Master Epps.

1443
01:47:07,135 --> 01:47:08,135
Now, you speak?

1444
01:47:08,261 --> 01:47:10,311
Now that you want
to add to her lies, you find your tongue!

1445
01:47:10,430 --> 01:47:12,680
I went to Master
Shaw's plantation.

1446
01:47:12,724 --> 01:47:14,354
Ah! You admit it.

1447
01:47:14,601 --> 01:47:16,021
Yes, freely.

1448
01:47:16,144 --> 01:47:18,024
And you know why?

1449
01:47:18,146 --> 01:47:20,606
I got this from Mistress Shaw.

1450
01:47:21,232 --> 01:47:25,202
Mistress Epps
won't even grant me no soap to clean with.

1451
01:47:25,653 --> 01:47:29,373
I stink so much,
I make myself gag!

1452
01:47:32,535 --> 01:47:35,745
500 pounds of cotton.

1453
01:47:36,081 --> 01:47:38,041
Day in, day out!

1454
01:47:38,208 --> 01:47:40,038
More than any man here.

1455
01:47:40,210 --> 01:47:42,210
And for that, I will be clean.

1456
01:47:42,379 --> 01:47:44,129
That's all I ask.

1457
01:47:44,255 --> 01:47:47,335
This, here, what I went to Shaw's for.

1458
01:47:48,677 --> 01:47:49,717
Liar.

1459
01:47:50,053 --> 01:47:53,523
The Lord knows that's all!

1460
01:47:53,640 --> 01:47:54,560
You're a liar.

1461
01:47:54,724 --> 01:47:58,234
And you,
blind with your own covetousness!

1462
01:47:59,145 --> 01:48:01,305
I don't lie, Master.

1463
01:48:01,731 --> 01:48:05,071
If you kill me,
I'll stick to that.

1464
01:48:05,735 --> 01:48:07,395
I'll fetch you down.

1465
01:48:08,238 --> 01:48:10,278
I'll learn you
to go to Shaw's.

1466
01:48:10,615 --> 01:48:11,735
Treach.

1467
01:48:13,743 --> 01:48:15,373
Run and fetch some line.

1468
01:48:15,495 --> 01:48:16,615
Edward!

1469
